com.joliciel.talismane.rawText

Class RawTextRegexAnnotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.rawText.RawTextRegexAnnotator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotator<AnnotatedText>, RawTextAnnotator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DuplicateWhiteSpaceFilter, NewlineEndOfSentenceMarker, NewlineSpaceMarker, OtherWhiteSpaceFilter

    public class RawTextRegexAnnotator
extends java.lang.Object
implements RawTextAnnotator
    For a given regex, finds any matches within the text, and adds the appropriate marker to these matches. If no group is provided, will match the expression as a whole.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
